each farmer has integre numer of 1ha peaces of ground.
Farmer can colect peaces into farmlands/orchards/pigsty/chickencoop/pasture/forest and then he can decice what he will produce on each peace
eg. i choose  to make orchand and on orchand i decide to make plums and apple

Farmers send to market products and theris prices.  Random generated consumers best (minimal) price*time_on_market  what they find.


1 day IRL is 7 days in game. 

